The Ottawa-Carleton Detention Centre is a correctional facility on [[Innes Road]] in [[Ottawa]], [[Ontario]].<ref name="homepage">[http://www.mcscs.jus.gov.on.ca/english/corr_serv/adult_off/facilities/det_centres/det_centres.html Ministry of Community Safety and Correctional Services]</ref> It opened in 1972.
